Feat: agent pause, run-every interval, prefix picker (v2.0.2)

Pause button in agent panel header: stops auto-runs after each generation
without disabling the agent. Manual runs and Direct Commands always fire
regardless of pause state.

Run every N messages: new input next to Main Lookback. Set to 5 to run
the agent once per 5 generations. Counter resets on chat change.
Defaults to 1 (every message).

Campaign prefix Pick button: opens a floating dropdown of all existing
world info books and auto-extracts the root prefix when clicked.
